Topic: Programming Concepts (Python-Based)
1️⃣ Clear Theory (Easy Language)

Programming is giving instructions to a computer.

Basic concepts:

Variables

Data Types

Operators

Conditions

Loops

Functions

2️⃣ Core Concepts
🔹 Variables

Store data

x = 10
name = "Akshay"
🔹 Data Types

int → numbers

float → decimal

str → text

bool → True/False

🔹 Operators

+, -, *, /

==, !=, >, <

🔹 Conditions
if x > 5:
    print("Yes")
🔹 Loops
for i in range(5):
    print(i)
🔹 Functions
def add(a, b):
    return a + b
🧠 Quick Tricks

Variable = storage

Loop = repeat

Function = reusable code

Condition = decision

